high_descs: Move forward, head around the corner to the right, to the side side of the coffee table with the computer on it.
Pick up the computer on the coffee table.
Bring the computer forward to the purple ottoman.
Put the computer on the ottoman, to the right of the keys.
anns.task_desc: Put a computer on the ottoman.

high_descs: Turn right, go to the wall, turn left, go forward, turn right at the couch, go forward, turn left and go to the coffee table
Close the laptop on the coffee table and pick it up
Go to the chair on the other side of the coffee table
Put the laptop on the leg rest in front of the chair
anns.task_desc: Bring the laptop to the leg rest

high_descs: Turn right, hang a left at the wall, turn right at the couch and turn left at the fireplace to walk to the wooden coffee table ahead.
Close the lid of the laptop computer and pick it up from the table.
Turn right, hang a left at the wall and walk to the ottoman of the black chair ahead.
Put the laptop computer on the right side of the ottoman near the chair.
anns.task_desc: Place a laptop computer on an ottoman.
